    <a href="#flow" class="nav-a"><span class="nav-dot"></span>完整数据流</a>
    <a href="#docs" class="nav-a"><span class="nav-dot"></span>文档索引</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="main">

<!-- ── Hero ── -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-tag">📦 osg-fe-ai-iframe / sku-agent</div>
  <h1>商品建档 Agent<br/><span>技术架构与设计文档</span></h1>
  <p>Keemart 芥末系统内嵌的 AI 商品建档助手。用户通过自然语言或上传 Excel/图片，由 AI Agent 自动完成商品批量建档的结构化数据填写，最终由商家确认后提交到芥末平台。</p>
  <div class="hero-meta">
    <span>📅 最后更新：2026-06-02</span>
    <span>👥 前端开发 · 架构评审 · 技术汇报</span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content">

<!-- ① 整体架构 -->
<div class="sec" id="arch">
  <div class="sec-hd">
    <div class="sec-num" style="background:var(--brand-light);color:var(--brand)">①</div>
    <div class="sec-title">整体架构</div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:14px">
    <div class="card-title">🏗️ 三层嵌套架构</div>
    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:9px">
      <div style="background:var(--g50);border:1px solid var(--g200);border-radius:9px;padding:13px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px">
        <div style="width:38px;height:38px;background:#fce7f3;border-radius:9px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:18px;flex-shrink:0">🏠</div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700">pc-w（osg-fe-jiemo-pc-w）</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--g500);margin-top:2px">外层主应用壳，负责全局 UI、鉴权、顶部导航</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="padding-left:20px;color:var(--g300);font-size:16px">└──</div>
      <div style="margin-left:20px;background:var(--blue-light);border:1px solid #bfdbfe;border-radius:9px;padding:13px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px">
        <div style="width:38px;height:38px;background:#dbeafe;border-radius:9px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:18px;flex-shrink:0">🤖</div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--blue)">ai-iframe（osg-fe-ai-iframe）</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--g500);margin-top:2px">AI Agent 容器层，GlobalEventService 常驻于此，Agent 切换时 SSE 连接不断开</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="padding-left:40px;color:var(--g300);font-size:16px">└──</div>
      <div style="margin-left:40px;background:var(--purple-light);border:1px solid #ddd6fe;border-radius:9px;padding:13px;display:flex;gap:11px">
        <div style="width:38px;height:38px;background:#ede9fe;border-radius:9px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:18px;flex-shrink:0">🏷️</div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--purple)">sku-agent（商品建档 Agent 业务层）</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--g500);margin-top:2px">ChatService / SessionService / TaskService 通过 bindServices 随组件生命周期自动创建/销毁</div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:7px;margin-top:8px;flex-wrap:wrap">
            <span style="font-size:10px;background:var(--blue-light);color:var(--blue);padding:2px 7px;border-radius:8px">shared/ 跨Agent公共能力</span>
            <span style="font-size:10px;background:var(--purple-light);color:var(--purple);padding:2px 7px;border-radius:8px">sku-agent/ 专属实现</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">⚙️ 技术栈</div>
    <div class="g4">
      <div class="stack"><div class="stack-lbl">UI 框架</div><div class="stack-val">React 18</div><div class="pill" style="background:#fce7f3;color:#9d174d">TypeScript</div></div>
      <div class="stack"><div class="stack-lbl">组件库</div><div class="stack-val">Keeta Design PC</div><div class="pill" style="background:var(--brand-light);color:var(--brand)">@sailor/keeta-design-pc</div></div>
      <div class="stack"><div class="stack-lbl">状态管理</div><div class="stack-val">RSJS</div><div class="pill" style="background:var(--blue-light);color:var(--blue)">@osgfe/rs-react</div></div>
      <div class="stack"><div class="stack-lbl">实时通信</div><div class="stack-val">SSE</div><div class="pill" style="background:var(--green-light);color:var(--green)">Fetch ReadableStream</div></div>
      <div class="stack"><div class="stack-lbl">工具库</div><div class="stack-val">@osgfe/tools</div><div class="pill" style="background:var(--amber-light);color:var(--amber)">含 lodash-es</div></div>
      <div class="stack"><div class="stack-lbl">国际化</div><div class="stack-val">i18n-web</div><div class="pill" style="background:var(--g100);color:var(--g600)">中 / EN / AR</div></div>
      <div class="stack"><div class="stack-lbl">样式</div><div class="stack-val">TailwindCSS</div><div class="pill" style="background:var(--g100);color:var(--g600)">+ CSS Module 兜底</div></div>
      <div class="stack"><div class="stack-lbl">构建</div><div class="stack-val">OBuilder</div><div class="pill" style="background:var(--g100);color:var(--g600)">pnpm dev/build</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ② UI 布局 -->
<div class="sec" id="layout">
  <div class="sec-hd">
    <div class="sec-num" style="background:var(--blue-light);color:var(--blue)">②</div>
    <div class="sec-title">UI 布局架构<small>三栏可拖拽</small></div>
  </div>
  <div class="ld">
    <div style="font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3);margin-bottom:10px;font-family:monospace">AppLayout（100dvh − TOP_NAVBAR_HEIGHT_PX）</div>
    <div class="ld-row">
      <div class="lp task">
        <div class="lp-name" style="color:#93c5fd">TaskPanel</div>
        <div class="lp-sub">左侧面板</div>
        <div class="lp-feat">📋 任务列表<br/>💬 会话列表<br/>🔔 待处理高亮</div>
        <div class="lp-range">10%~30%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="dh"></div>
      <div class="lp chat">
        <div class="lp-name" style="color:#6ee7b7">ChatArea</div>
        <div class="lp-sub">中间主区域（flex:1）</div>
        <div class="lp-feat">📝 历史消息 + 流式消息<br/>⏳ QueuePanel 排队浮层<br/>📎 输入框（含上传）<br/>🌐 EmbeddedBrowser（互斥）</div>
      </div>
      <div class="dh"></div>
      <div class="lp dlg">
        <div class="lp-name" style="color:#c4b5fd">Dialogue</div>
        <div class="lp-sub">右侧侧栏（可拖拽）</div>
        <div class="lp-feat">📊 EditableTable<br/>✅ 行内编辑 + 高亮<br/>📤 导出提交</div>
        <div class="lp-range">20%~50%</div>
      </div>
